        <item>
            <title>Version 0.0.10</title>
            <sparkle:version>0.0.10</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.0.10</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 03:02:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's Changed</h2>
<ul>
<li>appcast: v0.0.9 by <a href="https://github.com/apps/github-actions">@github-actions[bot]</a> in <a href="https://github.com/btucker/graftty/pull/92">#92</a></li>
<li>release: revert cask step to direct push (tap repo isn't protected) by <a href="https://github.com/btucker">@btucker</a> in <a href="https://github.com/btucker/graftty/pull/93">#93</a></li>
<li>fix(panes): override PATH so <code>graftty</code> resolves to the CLI (ATTN-4.2) by <a href="https://github.com/btucker">@btucker</a> in <a href="https://github.com/btucker/graftty/pull/94">#94</a></li>
<li>fix(pr-status): tighten poll cadence + cap backoff at 60s (PR-7.1, PR-7.2) by <a href="https://github.com/btucker">@btucker</a> in <a href="https://github.com/btucker/graftty/pull/95">#95</a></li>
<li>fix(sidebar): restore right-click menu on worktree rows (LAYOUT-2.7) by <a href="https://github.com/btucker">@btucker</a> in <a href="https://github.com/btucker/graftty/pull/97">#97</a></li>
<li>feat(worktree): non-blocking creation with placeholder + spinner (GIT-5.4..5.9) by <a href="https://github.com/btucker">@btucker</a> in <a href="https://github.com/btucker/graftty/pull/96">#96</a></li>
</ul>
<h2>New Contributors</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/apps/github-actions">@github-actions[bot]</a> made their first contribution in <a href="https://github.com/btucker/graftty/pull/92">#92</a></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href="https://github.com/btucker/graftty/compare/v0.0.9...v0.0.10">v0.0.9...v0.0.10</a></p>
]]></description>
